longTitle: TCGA breast invasive carcinoma (BRCA) miRNA gene expression by RNAseq (IlluminaHiseq)
dataProducer: British Columbia Cancer Agency TCGA genome characterization center
label: miRNA gene expression (IlluminaHiseq)
name: data/public/TCGA/BRCA/miRNA_HiSeq_gene
wrangling_procedure: Level_3 Data (file names: *.isoform.quantification.txt) download from TCGA DCC, for each sample, all isoform expression for the same miRNA gene are added together, log2(total_RPM +1) transformed, and deposited at UCSC into Xena repository.
